Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 並沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使煙花升空了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花 真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家邀請我來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 大家為了姐姐這麼盡心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 來接我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜呢 可能是別的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢 面麻覺得這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻正好最近喜歡看電視上播的Dodosuko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳知道什麼是Dodosuko嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}面麻沒能升天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為弄錯了願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要睡到樓上去睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在出來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓面麻發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得為什麼面麻沒能升天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為煙花 並不是面麻真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻沒能升天 不是因為弄錯了願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們真的是在為面麻著想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真心為了實現面麻的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只想到我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不願意看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳一直想著面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想讓面麻升天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想幫她實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了自己的私心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的私心被神明看透了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候開始 過了這麼長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我自己都很詫異我還是一如既往地喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只有宿海能看到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍受不了現在這種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不想讓面麻只屬於宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不如讓她的願望實現 升天了更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子你也好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再口是心非了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對雪集說什麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和不久前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也是 就你們兩個串通一氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要確認仁碳對面麻的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直嫉妒面麻 但你和我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是因為喜歡雪集而羨慕面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓面麻升天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有羨慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一開始我就知道我比不過面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奢求無法實現的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧 即使面麻升天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替代她的人也只會換成你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我做替代品其實根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 我從小一直羨慕的人是你啊 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候也是 現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是雪集的知心人 我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去向面麻告密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她那天你們會確認仁碳的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻事先知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 為什麼面麻一句話都沒提起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆把仁碳叫出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都說過要保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很過分吧 去說他們幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是面麻不僅喜歡仁碳 大家我都喜歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我就想 果然還是比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然花了很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我終於成了雪集的知心人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此我就知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在在雪集身邊的還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓面麻升天 安鳴和仁碳湊成一對的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就又可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著這些念頭 要讓面麻升天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼樣的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比什麼都不做要強多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要實現面麻的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她升天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻是不會原諒我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 面麻她…走的那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 好害怕當時在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想跑 可是怎樣也逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還住在了大家的秘密基地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去上高中而是滿世界亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想離得越遠就會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 還是會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們讓面麻升天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是自私的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就這種想法不一定能讓她升天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我無法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼前被水沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸消失在遠方的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法逃避啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓面麻升天 每個人都帶著私心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有認真地替面麻考慮她的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎 還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 回來晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太不在嗎 還在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 燈就這麼開著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的時候 仁太和超和平Busters的夥伴們在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近仁太比以前精神多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我去泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳最近啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳什麼的都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好和面麻道歉 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛…有兩道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 假睫毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我就覺得安鳴的眼睛有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃成那樣 不用再加假睫毛了吧 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴還是自然點好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過別再安鳴安鳴地亂叫了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家又開始互叫暱稱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我暗暗竊喜過只有我能看到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 面麻卻不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 我是認為沒能升天反而更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她想得不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是和我 也想和大家說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想升天之後轉世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真去實現面麻的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把面麻也叫出來 用日記本好好交流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和面麻一起 再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 撇開面麻在這說什麼都沒有意義 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們六個人一起 才是超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…那是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上把面麻帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秘密基地集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 我感覺我們終於開始向前邁進了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現你的願望 這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問心無愧地 讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.09,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終話 那個夏天盛開的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 面麻 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻的願望 好像已經實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仁碳的媽媽約好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳他是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為我變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直強忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然期待轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有這點我放不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他忍太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是希望他能多笑笑 多生生氣 多哭哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻向您保證 一定讓仁碳哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 面麻雖然想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻始終不知道該怎麼做好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓大家一起幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話把他們都叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}不是要讓大家欺負你讓你哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}面麻腦子笨 想讓大家用好一點的辦法讓你哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻她…不惜回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想實現的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…可終究還是不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著仁碳 是不是遭報應了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是報應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會去的啊 這和有沒有瞞著我沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時 無論如何我都會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 面麻其實是喜歡仁碳的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 到說再見的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還不行 再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只和我告別是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想 很想再見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你道聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你說「我喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大家都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你 等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個屬於我們的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻覺得好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要永遠和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至希望永遠能和仁碳像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道面麻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你在哪啊 快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 面麻 面麻！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…捉迷藏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}喂 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在和我們玩捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好好和大家告別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 怎麼樣 找到面麻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然面麻已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.88,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 波波 鶴子 安鳴 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…是日記的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這字…是面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鶴子 最喜歡溫柔的鶴子了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面…麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雪集 最喜歡努力的雪集了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「波波 最喜歡有趣的波波了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「安鳴 最喜歡獨立的安鳴了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最喜歡仁碳了 對仁碳的喜歡 是想成為仁碳的新娘的那種最喜歡」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次終於好好地告別了 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 不找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能算結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
