Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見你啊 面麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候 叫名字是不對的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻真不擅長玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 仁碳 好好說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 就能結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信 我們讀了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜歡你了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然也最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單方面的不算是告別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你替我實現了願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳又把面麻弄哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}弄哭了弄哭啦 去向老師告狀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 你這傢伙居然叛變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 怎麼能這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想再和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和大家…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 哭了哦 告別了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預…備…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 找到你啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻果然還是笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在慢慢長大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們走過的季節裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路旁盛開的花朵也在不斷變化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個季節盛開的花是…叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕搖曳著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一碰的話會微微刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近一聞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱約有股青澀的陽光的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那氣息漸漸地淡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在慢慢長大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朵花 一定還在某個地方盛開著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會繼續實現那朵花的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.64,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,146)}超和平Busters永遠是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:55.12,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,300)}{\frz12}ByeBye
